description: Search the curbs of the Derby City for The Kentucky Taco Company truck where this talented team is taking tasty comfort cuisine and serving it up in a warm tortilla.The Louisville locals are just loving this truck’s sensational selection of soul food creations, including the Roasted Pork Taco with tomato jam and smoked tomatillo sour cream, The Sloppy Joe Taco (and the vegan version), Fried Chicken & Mac & Beer Cheese, and more!For a most delicious handheld treat, come check out The Kentucky Taco Co.
name: The Kentucky Taco Co.
